systemd
Systemd Is a Default Init System For Triaxis

OpenRC
sudo apt install openrc

runit
sudo apt install runit

s6
sudo apt install s6

dinit
sudo apt search dinit

if available
sudo apt install dinit

If Triaxis doesnâ€™t ship Dinit yet

git clone https://github.com/davmac314/dinit.git
cd dinit
make
sudo make install

Switch Init System

sudo nano /etc/default/grub
Add:

For OpenRC
init=/sbin/openrc-init

For runit
init=/sbin/runit-init

For s6
init=/sbin/s6-svscan

For dinit
init=/sbin/dinit

sudo update-grub

Reboot and confirm With
ps -p 1 -o comm=
